# GKError.Code.notSupported

**Case**

The app doesn’t have Game Center enabled.

## Declaration

```swift
case notSupported
```

## Configuration Errors

- **GKError.Code.gameUnrecognized**: The system can’t complete the requested operation because Game Center doesn’t recognize the app.
- **GKError.Code.appUnlisted**: The system can’t complete the requested operation because the game isn’t available on the App Store.
